membership:
The IHEU is ECOSOC accredited and has consultative status with the United Nations. It also has observer status at the African Commission on Human and People's Rights and participatory status at the Council of Europe.&#xd;
&#xd;
We are also members of the UN NGO Committee on Human Rights (Geneva), UN NGO Committee on Freedom of Religion or Belief (Geneva), The Conference of Non-Governmental Organizations in Consultative Relationship with the United Nations (CoNGO), and the Conference of International Non-Governmental Organisations at the Council of Europe (INGO).

